  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a late night shift worker at a <i><strong>spooky </strong></i>library, what could possibly go wrong? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The library is <strong>haunted</strong>, danger lurks around every bookshelf. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Return the books and escape the library! </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Let Me Book</u> is a simple but <strong>intense</strong>, first-person survival game where your goal is to return the books<strong> </strong>to their bookshelves and not <u><strong>DIE</strong></u><strong> </strong>in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.poster.avif?t=1732865352\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.webm?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.mp4?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will have you experience a blend of <strong>tension,</strong> <strong>fear </strong>and <strong>dread,</strong> while using your wit, memory and skill to outsmart and out-maneuver the <strong>haunted entity</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.poster.avif?t=1732865352\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.webm?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.mp4?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What people have to say:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Whoa, that was intense!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"It was fun, dreadful and scary\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Simple game idea executed marvelously\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Truly scary\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"So anxiety inducing\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"DAMN I am even struggling to write!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Really solid horror game!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"There is a real tension as we shelve the books\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Works well to creep the player out\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"I was really at edge during the last books\"</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extra features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls Remapping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphics & Audio Options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets 🤫</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warnings:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epilepsy: contains some flashing lights and images.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gets pretty <strong>tense</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a late night shift worker at a <i><strong>spooky </strong></i>library, what could possibly go wrong? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The library is <strong>haunted</strong>, danger lurks around every bookshelf. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Return the books and escape the library! </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Let Me Book</u> is a simple but <strong>intense</strong>, first-person survival game where your goal is to return the books<strong> </strong>to their bookshelves and not <u><strong>DIE</strong></u><strong> </strong>in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.poster.avif?t=1732865352\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.webm?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/211e3a1e3fd6b9aca7f384e3ee84722c.mp4?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will have you experience a blend of <strong>tension,</strong> <strong>fear </strong>and <strong>dread,</strong> while using your wit, memory and skill to outsmart and out-maneuver the <strong>haunted entity</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.poster.avif?t=1732865352\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.webm?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225020/extras/c69dd67b2876567608f80558711b52a0.mp4?t=1732865352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What people have to say:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Whoa, that was intense!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"It was fun, dreadful and scary\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Simple game idea executed marvelously\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Truly scary\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"So anxiety inducing\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"DAMN I am even struggling to write!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Really solid horror game!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"There is a real tension as we shelve the books\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Works well to creep the player out\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"I was really at edge during the last books\"</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extra features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls Remapping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphics & Audio Options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets 🤫</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warnings:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epilepsy: contains some flashing lights and images.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gets pretty <strong>tense</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
